io.oasp.gastronomy.restaurant.tablemanagement.service.api.rest

Interface TablemanagementRestService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    RestService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TablemanagementRestServiceImpl

    @Path(value="/tablemanagement/v1")
@Named(value="TablemanagementRestService")
@Consumes(value="application/json")
@Produces(value="application/json")
public interface TablemanagementRestService
extends RestService
    The service class for REST calls in order to execute the methods in Tablemanagement.
